428
00:16:51,880 --> 00:16:53,327
Mais j'ai toujours eu le sentiment...

429
00:16:55,927 --> 00:16:56,748
ben, j'ai toujours eu le sentiment

430
00:16:56,749 --> 00:16:58,748
